Pre-Game Insights: Australia and Pakistan are both in need of a win in this match to boost their chances of qualifying for the semifinals.
The match is expected to be close, and the outcome may depend on which team performs better under pressure.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Australia had lost two consecutive matches to India and South Africa before finally getting a win on the board against Sri Lanka.
Pakistan, on the other hand, are coming off a loss to arch-rivals India in their previous match.
Others: Australia and Pakistan will face off in the 18th match of the ICC Cricket World Cup 2023 on Friday, October 20, 2023, at the M Chinnaswamy Stadium in Bengaluru.
